Articles.Content:
I lost 5 mun flights that ran out of fuel and decided to go completely overkill and ended up with this. Everything is done by staging except the SRBs. 1 will decouple the 8 small SRBs and 2 will decouple the 4 big SRBs.

Download: https://www.dropbox.com/sh/8nb7q9ymxkqqr9c/MGR_0GNCME

Some pictures: http://imgur.com/a/Z33fb

NOTE: This rocket was made in about 5 minutes so don't be suprised if something fails. I am checking things over and if I find anything big I will fix it.
